{"tid":1727702,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"（重整旗鼓）對家改哂策略，想陰死我地，我地要更高手段！","createTime":"2019-11-16T13:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T05:20:43.000Z","uid":43288,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"66c49b87f957068c2fe170761f9637f51a31fe12","tid":1727702,"uid":43288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:58:58.000Z","msg":"今日叫左老解出黎，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但佢地扮到好親民</span></span></strong>話比人聰解放軍一D都唔可怕，<br />\n溫水煮港豬。唔可以比佢地得程<br />\n加上有一班港豬藍C幫手清RB，成個畫面比外媒國際睇<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好似好和諧</span></span></strong><br />\n黑衫人阻人睇醫生做手術，火魔熱心清RB既市民(from NOW)。好似<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nSpin走哂成個星期既黎明行動既成果</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">重點！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n---------勇武<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">地區性前線引戰去狗舍，等放TG。唔放就火魔！即走！</span></span><br />\n燒狗車，攞神裝又好，麻包袋，點都要令佢地係壓力同恐怖下生活！<br />\n<br />\n---------文宣和理<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">放大二噁英嚴重性</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請專家對<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">重災區做Test</span></span>，<br />\n連儂牆再組織和理非全港清田潔香港大行動！<br />\n仲有就係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">二噁英，五百蚊一粒TG長輩圖</span></span>呢D咁好既材料，唔好用係同溫層，要係藍絲，離地港豬到Share 同輿論，服求要佢地割席<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好浪費呢幾日黎明行動手足既血同汗！<br />\n<br />\n仲有死左受傷被姦既手足，我地要為佢地復仇！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65042062904ce8bcc6b242691eef3c64347dd8c7","tid":1727702,"uid":43288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"f1e7bca0b0c8323531b